## <a name="pause-resume-stop-remove-or-otherwise-control-a-storyboard-interactively"></a><span data-ttu-id="f93c2-103">暂停、继续、停止、删除或以交互方式控制情节提要</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f93c2-103">Pause, Resume, Stop, Remove, or Otherwise Control a Storyboard Interactively</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="f93c2-104">若要能够以交互方式暂停、恢复、删除或以交互方式控制 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A>，请设置其 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> 属性，并使用 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> 对象（例如 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>或 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>）通过引用其 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>来控制它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f93c2-104">To be able to pause, resume, remove, or otherwise control a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> interactively, set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> property of its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> and use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> object (such as <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>, or <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>) to control it by referencing its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f93c2-105">如果未指定 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>，则在开始后无法以交互方式控制 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f93c2-105">If the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> is unspecified, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> cannot be interactively controlled after it is begun.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f93c2-106">有关详细信息，请参阅[如何：在演示图板启动后使用事件触发器控制情节提要](/dotnet/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f93c2-106">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](/dotnet/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts) for more information.</span></span>  
  
## <a name="when-to-remove-storyboards"></a><span data-ttu-id="f93c2-107">何时移除情节提要</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f93c2-107">When to Remove Storyboards</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="f93c2-108">应使用 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RemoveStoryboard> 操作删除以 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.HandoffBehavior.Compose><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.HandoffBehavior%2A> 开头的任何情节提要。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f93c2-108">You should use the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RemoveStoryboard> action to remove any storyboards begun with a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.HandoffBehavior%2A> of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.HandoffBehavior.Compose>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f93c2-109">当不再使用背景动画时，最好删除动画动画的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f93c2-109">It's also a good idea to remove background animations when the object they animate is no longer being used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f93c2-110">例如，如果使用元素的 <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Loaded> 事件应用无限重复的情节提要，还应创建一个 <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger>，该使用 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RemoveStoryboard> 操作删除元素的 <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Unloaded> 事件上的情节提要。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f93c2-110">For example, if you apply an indefinitely repeating storyboard using an element's <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Loaded> event, you should also create an <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> that uses a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RemoveStoryboard> action to remove the storyboard on the element's <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Unloaded> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
